{"tid":1133731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"夜媽媽見到啲咁嘅嘢","createTime":"2019-05-01T09:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T11:08:31.000Z","uid":143441,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"93b5a37240fc998e778be1a9aac081abe421c166","tid":1133731,"uid":143441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o8Y0uW0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo8Y0uW0.png&h=a536a3c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說尋晚同班朋友去bar飲一兩杯<br />\n走嗰陣見到啲好奇怪嘅嘢<br />\n離遠見到對面街夜媽媽有個高瘦女人企係度<br />\n遠睇仲可以好清楚咁睇到佢嘅頭髮，鼻同埋衫褲<br />\n成班朋友即刻晒淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GwhAiRY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGwhAiRY.png&h=c977e955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知行近啲睇原來只係一棵俾人斬咗嘅樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b9361067cdd8802d483801454a2016d9f47bc7","tid":1133731,"uid":96002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:56:04.000Z","msg":"安心<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776d5a0900d75cfa59937d78201f94645ecb1658","tid":1133731,"uid":237303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:57:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c777084c7dc8c828f00de648efab23cccc30dfc","tid":1133731,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4509ab2bb262adc8abdac47ec2985e15fa2ecd","tid":1133731,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c62d47ea7888576e57eab353ac73678b6a23a0","tid":1133731,"uid":218977,"like":0,"dislik